      "text": "あ、ありがとう。遙子の的確な指示のおかげだわ\nmihoさんの方はどうですか？　火は起こせました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T‚ thanks. It’s all thanks to Haruko’s precise instructions.\nHow about you‚ miho-san? Were you able to start a fire?",
        "id": ""
