      "text": "カメラが回ってるけど、大人の話を沢山しちゃうわよ！\n早速だけど、年下の子との距離感、どうしてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though the camera is rolling‚ I’m going to talk about lots of grown-up things!\nFirst things first‚ how do you manage the distance with your younger members?",
        "id": ""
      },
