      "text": "お姉さんとして威厳を持ちつつ、でも仲良くしたいから\n同じ目線に立つんだけど……距離感が難しいなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to maintain my dignity as a senior‚ but at the same time‚ I try to\nget on the same page with them to be friendly… It’s hard to find the right balance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.9667390942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
